                  terrapeer.vui.j3dui.utils.objects.TestTic
public class TestTic
extends javax.media.j3d.TransformGroup

Creates a standard test tic object that is a small box with a fixed translation. The tic size is 0.1 x 0.1 x 0.1. The color can be set at run time, and is purely emissive.
